name: FAKISTAN by PEPENARDO | Official Fake Rare | Series 8 Card 3 | 1/125
description:
FAKISTAN, portrays a reserved masked figure lounging on a magnificent green camel, wearing a patterned head covering and a white linen galabeya. His face is concealed from the viewer as he gazes into the reflection of his phone screen. In the distance, an ancient monument towers over the mystical landscape. It possesses a strange and arcane essence.

The title and more significantly, the imagined country, FAKISTAN, alludes to a controversial past; referencing a 4chan initiated sovereign order, KEKISTAN. However, FAKISTAN represents a new nation birthed out of the underground Fake Rare movement. It is populated by enlightened individuals such as innovators, artists, patrons, and philosophers whose goal is to uplift one another, while building towards a brighter future.

FAKISTAN will continue to carry the narrative and symbol of crypto.
